Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳可是這溫德布倫王國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一且正統的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家全部都屬於妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要那個娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，真白公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這種花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，真白公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫水，當馬給我騎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，真白公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白公主，上課時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個公主真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先王和王后明明那麼優秀\N真是一點也不像他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好那個傳聞\N是真的也說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，講這個不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難免會想去相信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真正的公主\N在那時候和那二位一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾泰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，是第五公子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，妳是真白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳就是傳聞中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌公主是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先王和先后…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一點也不像他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真正的公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好那個傳聞…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那時候和那二位一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過世了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是妳害的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是女王喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是溫德布倫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:03:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7話 蒼之舞／少女的契約\N給叔叔，今天放假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是每週最快樂的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有今天早上不用掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都可以稍微多睡一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就算是假日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也幾乎沒有人整天玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會練習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會唸書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫老師做事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者幫學姊打掃房間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家似乎都很忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實，我開始打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然叔叔說\N不需要顧慮錢的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得自己的事情\N還是要自己負責
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是慢慢來\N我還是想要還你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工工作是奈緒學姊介紹的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我很適合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息完之後\N聽說要到正門前集合喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔，那就先這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上工了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王今天可是特地\N親自前來慰勞我們喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你們的本事\N能夠蓋出一座很棒的城堡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然突然跑來視察
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可不是加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的工作成效如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個子雖小但是很賣力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有前途喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我好好工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，真是可愛的女王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家之後跟媽媽炫耀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那是什麼態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳來一下好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的信\N剛剛寄到辦公室的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡中庭的地方啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近倒是沒有什麼損害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊？真白女王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是傳聞中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程重做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把這座城堡\N徹底改建成一座新的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼現在才說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想讓大家過去的努力都泡湯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是本國之王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照我的意思去做\N有哪裡不對了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼任性妄為\N妳這樣還算是一個女王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭妳了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的打了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說一直沒看到她\N才追到這裡看看的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然碰到有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從很久以前就有這種傳聞\N圍繞著真白公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敷一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME的容貌也很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心別讓臉變得更扁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，陛下到底上哪去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是距今14年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賊人入侵這個風華宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪去國王和王妃的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不湊巧地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服侍國王的乙HiME才剛剛退休
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人阻止得了賊人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很清楚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我在這裡留學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛出生的公主下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正當衆人放棄她的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時的內務大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到現在的真白公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說她才是真正的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據來自大臣捉到的“犯人”\N所說的證詞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到大臣也過世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主即位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都假裝忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣的傳聞卻從來沒消失過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳也想當乙HiME的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是慎選服侍的對象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟契約是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，螞蟻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回頭會洗乾淨還你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家其實都在笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，找～到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，找妳好久喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這種臉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是來講很重要的事耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫德布倫王國女王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白·布蘭·杜·溫德布倫陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說這種話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該上哪找…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的貴石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突…突然胡說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白也喜歡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰喜歡你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見面的時候也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我，我要叫人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次見到妳的時候\N就一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為妳而傾倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆說過\N不可以強迫人家做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我先投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，再會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本用不著妳救…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這座宮殿玩起捉迷藏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人比得過真白女王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這樣講
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在即位之前\N就一直有人想對公主不利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有個萬一的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說黑團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟普通鄰居\N很有可能因為一封黑色的信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不得自省，化身為破壞者吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想太多了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白在王座房裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有點生氣就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？這是妳的城耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座城可是有\N將近三百年的歷史耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才14歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣算的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是沒大腦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二王戰爭的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為還保有很多這種機械
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才造成悲慘的戰爭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳連這個都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我現在在學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這場戰爭劃下休止符的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是持有“純白的金鋼石”的\N第一位乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是妳們的真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父王跟母后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那個貴石為基礎取的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點羨慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從懂事的時候就沒有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很喜歡“愛莉卡”這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不知道\N是不是他們幫我取的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，就算這樣，我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是夢宮愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，真白也是真白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不會是想安慰我\N給我打氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓妳這種人同情\N那我也完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命，跑太前面的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡地底下竟然有這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心，我只是看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是…管風琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼處理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠，還不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠是什麼不夠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得到這座古風琴（Harmonium）的力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須齊備歌\N編織者跟守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃，會被關在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要咧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來我們長年的願望就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，快點出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳打算怎麼處理這個貴石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂～\N歌和編織者與守護者？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才都跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有好多事情想做耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳幹嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，左手借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，還有就是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，契約跟認證
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳認同我為主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原則上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫原則上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼愛莉卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名解放汝之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，上陣啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來可以飛啊，好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來妳成為Meister-乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為夠資格能夠\N服侍主人的乙HiME時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:20:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會透過GEM與主人共有生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽，拜託妳，借我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個陰沈的老兄呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個姑娘也沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，最近的年輕人喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，還是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來只能向加爾德羅貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳快點走開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦，這也是沒辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事情要保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然跟妳訂了契約…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳說要訂的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之妳要負起\N找出解除契約方法的責任喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大～對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:23:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.77,0:23:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求婚失敗了\N（命運之軛）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.64,0:23:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重點在於衝勁上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱住之後就應該馬上這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個男人在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.88,0:23:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.88,0:23:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，這是練習啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
